Text:
Goon Affiliated is the fourth studio album by American rapper Plies. The album 
is scheduled for release by Atlantic Records on June 8, 2010...

The song "Look Like", which features rap verses from Young Jeezy & Fabolous is 
the first song on any of Plies' albums to feature other rappers... The bonus 
tracks i just like so i put them on... Peace all... 

---
